item.description:
Update package database sudo apt update
Upgrade installed packages sudo apt upgrade
Install a package sudo apt install &lt;package name&gt;
Uninstall a package sudo apt remove &lt;package name&gt;
or
sudo apt purge
Note : remove leaves configuration files, purge removes all files related to the package
Search for package apt search &lt;search string&gt;
List installed packages apt list &ndash;installed
or
dpkg -l
Show package information apt info &lt;package name&gt;
List package content apt show &lt;package name&gt;
